# Licensing

This repository contains three categories of content, each released under a separate license. To find the terms that apply to a given file, see the table below or the per-category license files.

| Content                                              | License        | File                  |
|------------------------------------------------------|----------------|-----------------------|
| Source code (`*.py`, `Makefile`, CI configs, etc.)   | MIT            | `LICENSE-CODE`        |
| Manuscript and figures                               | CC-BY-4.0      | `LICENSE-MANUSCRIPT`  |
| Data files (`*.csv`, `*.json`, screening log, etc.)  | CC-BY-4.0      | `LICENSE-DATA`        |

When in doubt, the most restrictive of the applicable licenses governs. All licenses require attribution; see `CITATION.cff` for the canonical citation.

